  2. Sat Apr. 13

    Rabies Clinic - Whitehall All Dogs and Cats should be vaccinated against rabies at 3 months of age and re-vaccinated one year later, then every three years thereafter. Ferrets should be vaccinated against rabies at 3 months of age and re-vaccinated yearly thereafter. Please bring proof of any previous rabies vaccination. Pets must remain in vehicle until after registration. All pets need to be on a leash or in a carrier.
